th 197,471 votes. He is spokesperson of both [[Hope fraction]] and The Ninety Point Commission in the parliament. He was a former member of [[Shiraz]]'s city council, being elected in [[Iranian local elections, 2013|2013 local election]], but was resigned on 15 June 2015 in favor of stand at the parliamentary election.
