{{No footnotes|date=April 2009}} '''Fegime''', or '''Fédération Européenne des Grossistes Indépendants en Matériel Electrique''' (European Federation of Independent Electrical Wholesalers) is a business alliance. It assists member companies for gaining and fulfilling international contracts. As of early 2005 Fegime claims a membership of 162 companies in nine countries including the [[United Kingdom]], [[Germany]], [[Italy]] and [[Spain]] with a total turnover of €1.8 billion.
